Good morning, Raffaella.

I hope my email finds you well.

I am responding to your query/email on 27/08/25 regarding the privacy reque=
st you put in.

I have asked for this to be followed up with our privacy team, I can see th=
e Senior Claim Manager has provided the information requested to our privac=
y team on 25/07/25. So I ill get this followed up for you.

Where you mention you want updated copies of your claim file provided to yo=
u monthly. Can you elaborate on what exactly you are wanting? Are you wanti=
ng the entire claim file sent to you each month as we get new information? =
Or just the updated information?

Regarding the contents claim, I am just waiting on approval from our team t=
o proceed with finalizing your claim. As soon as I get this I will contact =
you via email to finalize. I am trying to get this through urgently for you=
.

Kind regards,

Zach




Zach Pion
Complex Claims Management Consultant | Tower
DDI +64 9 960 4527| 0800 808 808 ext: 59210
Level 5, 136 Fanshawe Street, PO Box 90347, Auckland 1142
zach.pion@tower.co.nz<mailto:zach.pion@tower.co.nz> | tower.co.nz<http://ww=
w.tower.co.nz/>
