/>.

From: Claims
Sent: Thursday, August 21, 2025 10:56 AM
To: raffaellanz@icloud.com
Subject: Contents Claim: #C90306256 - damaged contents

Good morning, Maria.

I hope my email finds you well.

My email is just to update you that I have taken over both your contents cl=
aim and your house claim C90306048.

Currently I am working on the list of contents items Asset Restore has prov=
ided Tower.

Once I can get through this list, I will flick you an email to update you r=
egarding the next steps of the claim.

Any questions please ask.

Kind regards,

Zach

Zach Pion
Complex Claims Management Consultant | Tower
DDI +64 9 960 4527| 0800 808 808 ext: 59210
Level 5, 136 Fanshawe Street, PO Box 90347, Auckland 1142
zach.pion@tower.co.nz<mailto:zach.pion@tower.co.nz> | tower.co.nz<http://ww=
